videos.description: Stephanie Mavunga grabs the offensive rebound and finds a cutting Asia Doss, who lays it in and draws a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Ohio State's Doss gets 3-point play) 2018/0107 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ohio State's Doss gets 3-point play

videos.description: Linnae Harper jumps ahead of the pass and takes it herself for a fast-break layup.
videos.headline: Harper's steal leads to Ohio State layup

videos.description: Katelynn Flaherty throws a long lead pass to Hallie Thome, who beats defenders for a transition layup.
videos.headline: Thome gets behind defense for Michigan layup

videos.description: Hallie Thome splits two defenders and lays it in to bring Michigan within a point.
videos.headline: Thome spins for layup

videos.description: Hallie Thome delivers an elbow to Alex Hart during a one-on-one matchup and picks up an unsportsmanlike foul for the physical play.
videos.headline: Thome call for unsportsmanlike foul

videos.description: Katelynn Flaherty drives by two Ohio State defenders and lays it in for the game-tying bucket.
videos.headline: Flaherty ties game for Michigan

videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell gets her defender to fall back with a hard jab step and nails a 3-pointer to give Ohio State a 2-point lead.
videos.headline: Mitchell fools defender, drains 3

videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell takes it all the way herself for a layup to tie the game with 12 seconds remaining.
videos.headline: Mitchell goes coast-to-coast for game-tying bucket

videos.description: Kelsey Mitchell drains a deep 3-pointer with a defender in her face for Ohio State's first bucket in overtime.
videos.headline: Mitchell knocks down long 3-pointer

videos.description: Ohio State's leading scorer Kelsey Mitchell makes a layup but has to leave the game after awkward landing.
videos.headline: Mitchell leaves game after ankle injury
